<ul>
 <li>Web sites want to display dynamic content based on user and session
   <ul>
    <li>easiest to build with HTML editors</li>
    <li>need to mix the "static" content of HTML files with "directives" for accessing or generating dynamic content</li>
    <li>Java Server Pages meet this need</li>
   </ul>
 </li>
 <li>Key aspects of Java Server Pages:
   <ul>
    <li>Servlets</li>
    <li>JavaBeans</li>
    <li>Syntax </li>
   </ul>
</ul>
